    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界曾经是一个清朗美丽的地方，到处充满了光明和奇迹。但是有一天，一股邪恶的力量席卷了整个大地，夺走了世界的光明，让它陷入黑暗。结果，混乱和毁灭蔓延到整个世界，许多人担心黑暗将永无终结之日。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/cd3c84bfd038217d747fc91b4e57fccc.avif?t=1762838079\" width=620 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/63ebca24ffbd2c6d31dd0bdb1d27eb3f.poster.avif?t=1762838079\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/63ebca24ffbd2c6d31dd0bdb1d27eb3f.webm?t=1762838079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/63ebca24ffbd2c6d31dd0bdb1d27eb3f.mp4?t=1762838079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款动作roguelike游戏中，你要在每层塔中使用自动武器攻击，在成群的怪物攻势中生存下来。闪避并收集战利品，以提高下一轮获胜的几率。游戏的关键在于决策、反应和巧妙的移动。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/b20682688116aee557a211d6825b4f92.avif?t=1762838079\" width=620 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/c9a5665270668c7d4ded31dadc1a5674.poster.avif?t=1762838079\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/c9a5665270668c7d4ded31dadc1a5674.webm?t=1762838079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342950/extras/c9a5665270668c7d4ded31dadc1a5674.mp4?t=1762838079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集武器和配件并战略性地将它们整理到物品栏中对你的生存至关重要。你的物品栏空间有限，因此在放入新物品之前，你需要考虑其优缺点以及如何与你的整体战略相匹配。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对物品栏的精心管理可以决定胜负。随着游戏的进行，你将积累强大的武器和配件，使你成为不可阻挡的力量。</p>",
